title: Live Performance Dave Grohl and Nandi Bushell at The Forum LA jamming Everlong with Foo Fighters
author: Nandi Bushell
description: It Happened!!! It was EPIC!!! Thank you so much @Foo Fighters Thank you to everyone who made it possible for me to jam with Mr. Grohl -  Its my Daddy who filmed the video and is screaming a lot.
